 It's a physical chess game.</i>

48:48.324 --> 48:49.459
It makes her think.

48:49.492 --> 48:51.260
Demi: <i>
 Any time I'm able to</i>

48:51.293 --> 48:52.996
<i> take my mind off of...</i>

48:53.028 --> 48:55.130
any of my addictions, um,

48:55.164 --> 48:57.467
it's very beneficial to me.

48:57.500 --> 49:01.137
<i> Because you're constantly
 thinking about...</i>

49:01.170 --> 49:04.240
<i> what the next move is.</i>

49:04.273 --> 49:06.409
<i> The technique,</i>

49:06.442 --> 49:08.077
<i> the strategy,</i>

